        <name>insideAndOutside</name>
        <qualifiedname>MR.InSphereSearchSettings.insideAndOutside</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>if false then searches for the maximal inscribed sphere in mesh; if true then searches for both a) maximal inscribed sphere, and b) maximal sphere outside the mesh touching it at two points; and returns the smaller of two, and if it is b) then with minus sign </para>
